combating climate
change.

00:26.826 --> 00:31.564 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then: the latest unraveling in
the Russia
investigation.

00:31.598 --> 00:36.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Vladimir Putin admits that
Russian hackers
may have acted independently to
influence

00:36.936 --> 00:40.073 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
