President Trump decided
against moving the U.S. Embassy
in Israel

03:39.953 --> 03:43.323 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem, at
least for now.

03:43.356 --> 03:48.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
