04:50.556 --> 04:55.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But what is most important, I'm
deeply convinced
that any hackers cannot
significantly influence

04:55.261 --> 04:57.397 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
an election campaign in another
country.

04:57.430 --> 05:01.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Putin also called
President
Trump -- quote -- "a
straightforward person,

05:01.701 --> 05:05.338 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a frank person with a fresh set
of eyes."

05:05.371 --> 05:10.610 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Afghans buried loved ones today
after Wednesday's
massive truck bombing in Kabul.

05:10.643 --> 05:13.246 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The blast killed at least 90
people.

05:13.279 --> 05:16.883 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hundreds gathered today for the
funeral of
a security guard.

05:16.916 --> 05:23.690 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The bombing was one of the worst
attacks since
the 2014 drawdown of foreign
forces in Afghanistan.

05:23.723 --> 05:30.096 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A gunman caused a scare today at
a resort
complex in the capital of the
Philippines.

05:30.129 --> 05:32.332 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Reports of gunshots touched off
panic.

05:32.365 --> 05:36.135 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, in Washington, President
Trump called
it a terrorist attack.

05:36.169 --> 05:41.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A short time later, Manila
police announced
that it wasn't terrorism, and
that no one

05:41.174 --> 05:42.942 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
was hurt.

05:42.975 --> 05:49.582 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He said gunman fired into the
air, stole gambling
chips and set fire to gaming
tables.

05:49.615 --> 05:53.319 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The upcoming election in Britain
is turning
into a free-for-all.

05:53.353 --> 05:58.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
