week's bombing
in Manchester.

06:04.263 --> 06:08.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Prime Minister Theresa May
called the snap
election in order to bolster her
government

06:08.568 --> 06:12.739 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
