Wednesday that it
shows racism is very much alive.

06:54.414 --> 06:58.384 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LEBRON JAMES, Cleveland
Cavaliers: No matter
how much money you got, no
matter how famous

06:58.418 --> 07:03.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
you are, no matter how many
people admire
you, at the end of the day,
being a black

07:03.523 --> 07:06.993 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
man in America is very
frightening.

07:07.026 --> 07:11.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it lets us know that we have
got so much
farther, so much farther to go
to be equal

07:11.631 --> 07:13.299 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in this country.

