of this day,
the president's decision to
withdraw from

07:55.374 --> 07:59.912 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a global accord aimed at slowing
the impact
of climate change.

07:59.946 --> 08:05.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We explore the consequences of
all this, and
how it may play out in coming
years in the

08:05.318 --> 08:07.587 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
