Governor Jerry Brown,
a Democrat.

08:11.691 --> 08:17.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
His state is battling efforts by
the Trump
administration to roll back some
emissions

08:17.063 --> 08:18.731 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
