08:35.681 --> 08:36.849 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

08:36.883 --> 08:38.084 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JERRY BROWN (D), California: I
certainly do
mean that.

08:38.117 --> 08:40.553 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
