08:40.586 --> 08:47.560 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Climate change is an existential
threat to
all of humanity, to the natural
systems on

08:47.593 --> 08:49.795 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
