08:49.829 --> 08:55.868 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Not tomorrow, but starting very
quickly, we're
seeing changes.

08:55.902 --> 08:59.472 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
California has lost 100 million
trees from
the drought.

08:59.505 --> 09:01.274 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Sea level is rising.

09:01.307 --> 09:07.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the Antarctica is seeing ice
melting at an
ever rapid rate, some say in an
irreversible

09:07.747 --> 09:08.714 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
way.

09:08.748 --> 09:11.350 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is a profoundly serious
problem.

09:11.384 --> 09:17.757 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Paris agreement was an
agreement of nations
saying what they could do
voluntarily.

09:17.790 --> 09:19.892 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Here's the commitment.

09:19.926 --> 09:23.095 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
President Obama made something I
thought was
doable, was reasonable.

09:23.129 --> 09:29.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In fact, California is doing
that very thing
now, and our economy has grown
in terms of

09:29.235 --> 09:32.972 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
