nation as a
whole.

09:33.005 --> 09:34.607 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We have created over two million
jobs.

09:34.640 --> 09:35.608 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Yes.

09:35.641 --> 09:36.809 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

09:36.842 --> 09:39.679 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JERRY BROWN: So, climate action
and jobs go
together.

09:39.712 --> 09:45.084 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, that's why I say this move
by Trump makes
no sense, and it's going to hurt
America,

09:45.117 --> 09:47.620 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
