the reverse.

09:47.653 --> 09:50.056 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, as you
know, he makes
a different argument.

09:50.089 --> 09:54.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
