favor of doing
something to help the
environment, but he

09:55.027 --> 10:00.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
said this accord is going to
cost millions
of jobs and cost the American
people trillions

10:00.833 --> 10:02.234 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in lost economic output.

10:02.268 --> 10:03.235 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

10:03.269 --> 10:08.074 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JERRY BROWN: That's just --
that's a lie.

10:08.107 --> 10:09.875 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
