net, we have
added 2.4 million jobs in the
last eight years,

10:24.357 --> 10:26.292 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
since the recession.

10:26.325 --> 10:32.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That is a remarkable outcome,
and it's consistent,
in fact, I would say driven by
the clean tech

10:32.898 --> 10:38.304 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
investments and the climate
action strategies
that we have embarked upon.

10:38.337 --> 10:40.940 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, President Trump is
completely wrong.

10:40.973 --> 10:44.310 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's doing this for his own
base, highly ideological.

10:44.343 --> 10:46.846 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He's wrong on the science.

10:46.879 --> 10:47.847 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
He's wrong on the facts.

10:47.880 --> 10:49.815 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

10:49.849 --> 10:53.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, he also --
another argument
he makes, Governor, he says,
this puts restrictions

10:53.319 --> 10:59.191 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
on the United States, while the
United States
is reducing its emissions, while
it lets other

10:59.225 --> 11:04.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
