11:06.432 --> 11:07.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

11:07.433 --> 11:09.802 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JERRY BROWN: He really distorts
the record.

11:09.835 --> 11:12.605 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
