to do a lot
more.

11:43.069 --> 11:47.973 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, Trump is taking this in the
exact wrong
direction, which will cost us
more money.

11:48.007 --> 11:53.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When the New York, the subway is
underwater,
or New Orleans or President
Trump's hotel

11:53.145 --> 11:59.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
down there in Florida are
devastated by rising
sea levels, that will cost
hundreds of billions.

11:59.685 --> 12:02.922 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
