talking trillions.

12:02.955 --> 12:08.360 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, the economics is all to the
opposite of
what President Trump is saying.

12:08.394 --> 12:13.899 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Governor, among
other things,
as you know, the president is
talking to his

12:13.933 --> 12:15.334 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
