12:27.213 --> 12:28.447 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

12:28.481 --> 12:31.183 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JERRY BROWN: Well, I don't think
that message
is clear enough.

12:31.217 --> 12:33.486 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And certainly people can be more
articulate.

12:33.519 --> 12:35.888 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
California, obviously, it's
