Trump.

12:41.694 --> 12:47.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think part of that is our
environmental
policies working, as well as our
job creation

12:47.767 --> 12:49.502 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
running at full speed.

12:49.535 --> 12:55.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, yes, this is a message that
has to be
made more persuasively, more
simply, and made

12:55.341 --> 12:57.476 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
more extensively across the
country.

12:57.510 --> 13:01.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You mentioned
California, and
I think you said in your
statement today California

13:01.580 --> 13:08.788 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
