Donald Trump.

14:07.313 --> 14:13.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He has given a body blow to the
cause of environmental
sustainability, but we will take
it and we

14:13.619 --> 14:14.854 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
