14:22.595 --> 14:23.562 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

14:23.596 --> 14:25.264 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JERRY BROWN: Thank you.

14:25.297 --> 14:29.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
