14:51.624 --> 14:52.591 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

14:52.625 --> 14:55.060 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MIKE LEE (R), Utah: Yes, I think
