this ratified, in order to make
it the law

15:21.253 --> 15:23.255 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of the land as a governing
treaty.

15:23.289 --> 15:25.157 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
