with it.

15:33.632 --> 15:37.469 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump did that today
because he
decided this wasn't in the
interest of the

15:37.503 --> 15:38.637 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
