agreement.

16:33.659 --> 16:38.063 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, this has happened through
innovation,
through free market forces.

16:38.097 --> 16:42.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think quite the opposite of
what Governor
Brown was saying, that when the
government

16:42.067 --> 16:45.404 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
