squelch innovation.

16:45.437 --> 16:47.673 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that innovation is needed
for us to control
emissions.

16:47.706 --> 16:52.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Let me quote
