17:28.747 --> 17:30.616 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And, in fact, I think they're
inappropriate.

17:30.649 --> 17:34.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Again, we have to get back to
the fact that
this power, the power to enter
into binding

17:34.420 --> 17:37.322 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
