17:37.356 --> 17:42.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is something that was
decided, should
be a shared power, at the
Constitutional Convention

17:42.361 --> 17:44.463 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
